        "subject": "LU-12287 lnet: handling device failure by IB event handler",
        "message": "LU-12287 lnet: handling device failure by IB event handler\n\nThe following IB events cannnot be handlled by QP event handler\n- IB_EVENT_DEVICE_FATAL\n- IB_EVENT_PORT_ERR\n- IB_EVENT_PORT_ACTIVE\n\nIB event handler handles device errors such as hardware errors\nand link down.\n\nSigned-off-by: Tatsushi Takamura <takamr.tatsushi@jp.fujitsu.com>\nChange-Id: I19c39eda0b296b3dceb6b8e88f5b205a461c2e51\n"
